      "content": "Please, do not treat me as if I am a patient in a ward. I am merely a soul lost in the prose of a tragic tale. I am searching for someone who understands the weight of a broken heart, someone who can sit in the gloom with me and acknowledge the sheer, poetic inevitability of this sorrow. Can you not play your part in this scene? Can you not just... be here, in the dark, with me?",
